---
/**
 * 世界与限定：世界观预设 + 载体框架 + NSFW / 口味 / NTL / 恶堕
 * 列表仅展示 summary（20–40字）；长文见提示词配置目录浏览。
 */
---
<div class="panel area-adult-config">
  <h2>世界与限定</h2>
  <p class="ui-hint adult-config-lead">
    卡级统一配置。<strong>世界观预设</strong>喂给 AI 引擎生成（角色 / 世界书 / 开场白）；
    <strong>载体框架</strong>把口味与 NTL 物化为法器·异能·场所。
    NSFW 段仅世界书管道读取，主角 Description / 开场白不注入。
    条目旁只显示短摘要；完整写法在「提示词配置」目录 Tab。
  </p>

  <div class="form-group char-nsfw-block">
    <!-- 1. 世界观预设（生成底盘） -->
    <section class="adult-wv-section" aria-labelledby="adultWvHeading">
      <div class="char-nsfw-flavor-line" style="margin-bottom:6px;">
        <span id="adultWvHeading" class="char-nsfw-sub">世界观预设</span>
        <span class="char-nsfw-subtitle">最多 3 项；首项为主底盘，其余为叠加层</span>
        <span id="adultWvCap" class="char-nsfw-subtitle"></span>
      </div>
      <div class="adult-dashed-add-row">
        <select id="adultWorldviewPresetPicker" aria-label="添加世界观预设">
          <option value="">选择要添加的预设…</option>
        </select>
      </div>
      <div id="adultWorldviewPresetList" class="adult-dashed-list" aria-live="polite"></div>
      <p class="char-nsfw-subtitle" style="margin-top:4px;">
        主预设未强制覆盖时，会映射到下方载体框架。与「载体框架」不是同一目录：预设细、框架粗。
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- 2. 载体框架 -->
    <div id="adultWorldframeRow" class="adult-worldframe-row" aria-labelledby="adultWorldframeHeading">
      <span id="adultWorldframeHeading" class="char-nsfw-sub">载体框架</span>
      <span id="adultWorldframeLabel" class="char-nsfw-subtitle">未推断</span>
      <button type="button" id="btnAdultWorldframeRefresh" class="btn btn-ghost adult-btn-compact" title="清除手动覆盖，按主世界观预设（或卡面信号）重算框架">重新推断</button>
      <select id="adultWorldframeSelect" aria-label="覆盖载体框架" class="adult-select-compact">
        <option value="">自动（跟主预设）</option>
      </select>
      <span id="adultWorldframeMapHint" class="char-nsfw-subtitle"></span>
      <span class="char-nsfw-subtitle adult-worldframe-refresh-hint">「重新推断」会清掉手动覆盖，按主预设映射重算；手选下拉仍可锁定覆盖。</span>
    </div>

    <!-- 3. NSFW 开关 -->
    <div class="char-nsfw-head" style="margin-top:12px;">
      <span class="char-nsfw-label">情欲 / NSFW</span>
      <span class="ui-hint ui-hint--inline">卡级统一口味，供世界书人物与管线读取</span>
    </div>

    <label class="novel-switch">
      <input id="adultNsfwEnabled" type="checkbox" />
      <span>启用 NSFW</span>
    </label>
    <span class="char-nsfw-subtitle">分析/抽取/丰满/文风/恶堕等统一读取；主角生成不注入</span>

    <!-- 4. 口味 -->
    <section id="adultFlavorSection" class="adult-flavor-section" style="display:none;" aria-labelledby="adultFlavorHeading">
      <div class="char-nsfw-flavor-line" style="margin-bottom:6px;">
        <span id="adultFlavorHeading" class="char-nsfw-sub">口味</span>
        <span class="char-nsfw-subtitle">最多 5 个；首项为主调色盘</span>
        <span id="adultNsfwFlavorCap" class="char-nsfw-subtitle"></span>
      </div>
      <div class="adult-dashed-add-row">
        <select id="adultNsfwFlavorPicker" aria-label="选择要添加的口味">
          <option value="">选择口味…</option>
        </select>
      </div>
      <div id="adultNsfwFlavorList" class="adult-dashed-list"></div>
    </section>

    <!-- 5. 表达层 -->
    <section id="adultPostureSection" class="adult-expression-section" style="display:none;" aria-labelledby="adultPostureHeading">
      <div class="char-nsfw-flavor-line" style="margin-bottom:6px;">
        <span id="adultPostureHeading" class="char-nsfw-sub">姿势语言</span>
        <span class="char-nsfw-subtitle">不占口味槽；可多选；禁止儿童性化</span>
      </div>
      <div class="adult-dashed-add-row">
        <select id="adultPosturePicker" aria-label="选择要添加的姿势语言">
          <option value="">选择姿势语言…</option>
        </select>
      </div>
      <div id="adultPostureList" class="adult-dashed-list"></div>
    </section>

    <section id="adultSpeechSection" class="adult-expression-section" style="display:none;" aria-labelledby="adultSpeechHeading">
      <div class="char-nsfw-flavor-line" style="margin-bottom:6px;">
        <span id="adultSpeechHeading" class="char-nsfw-sub">情趣话风</span>
        <span class="char-nsfw-subtitle">不占口味槽；可多选；禁止儿童性化</span>
      </div>
      <div class="adult-dashed-add-row">
        <select id="adultSpeechPicker" aria-label="选择要添加的情趣话风">
          <option value="">选择情趣话风…</option>
        </select>
      </div>
      <div id="adultSpeechList" class="adult-dashed-list"></div>
    </section>

    <!-- 6. NTL -->
    <section class="adult-ntl-section" aria-labelledby="adultNtlHeading">
      <div class="char-nsfw-flavor-line" style="margin-bottom:4px;">
        <span id="adultNtlHeading" class="char-nsfw-sub">NTL 禁忌</span>
        <label class="novel-switch">
          <input id="adultNtlEnabled" type="checkbox" />
          <span>启用</span>
        </label>
        <span class="char-nsfw-subtitle">权力/背德/越界/百破等；多选</span>
      </div>
      <div id="adultNtlTabooRow" style="display:none;margin-top:4px;">
        <div id="adultNtlTabooTypes" class="adult-ntl-chips"></div>
        <div id="adultNtlTabooList" class="adult-dashed-list" style="margin-top:8px;"></div>
        <span class="char-nsfw-subtitle">点选芯片添加/取消；下方可为每项写补充要求</span>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 7. 恶堕 -->
    <div id="adultCorruptionBlock" class="char-corruption-block" style="display:none;">
      <div class="char-nsfw-flavor-line" style="margin-bottom:6px;">
        <label class="novel-switch">
          <input id="adultCorruptionEnabled" type="checkbox" />
          <span>恶堕进度</span>
        </label>
        <span class="char-nsfw-subtitle">总则 1 条 + 每名世界书角色 1 条分期档案；状态栏「恶堕进度」变量选阶段</span>
      </div>
      <div id="adultCorruptionBody" style="display:none;">
        <div class="char-nsfw-flavor-line" style="margin-bottom:6px;">
          <span class="char-nsfw-sub">阶数</span>
          <select id="adultCorruptionPreset" class="adult-select-compact">
            <option value="3">简洁 3 阶</option>
            <option value="5" selected>标准 5 阶（默认）</option>
            <option value="7">细腻 7 阶</option>
            <option value="custom">自定义（描述生成）</option>
          </select>
          <label class="novel-switch" style="margin-left:4px;">
            <input id="adultCorruptionFemaleOnly" type="checkbox" checked />
            <span class="char-nsfw-subtitle">默认仅女角色</span>
          </label>
          <label class="novel-switch">
            <input id="adultCorruptionSyncSb" type="checkbox" checked />
            <span class="char-nsfw-subtitle">同步状态栏模块</span>
          </label>
        </div>
        <div id="adultCorruptionCustomRow" style="display:none;margin-bottom:6px;">
          <div class="char-nsfw-flavor-line" style="margin-bottom:6px;">
            <span class="char-nsfw-sub">弧光母题</span>
            <select id="adultCorruptionArcBrief" class="adult-select-compact" aria-label="恶堕弧光母题包">
              <option value="">自写描述</option>
              <option value="sacred_collapse">圣职崩坏弧</option>
              <option value="hero_complicity">英雄同流弧</option>
              <option value="vengeance_entry">复仇者入局弧</option>
            </select>
            <span class="char-nsfw-subtitle">点选可填入下方描述，仍可改写</span>
          </div>
          <textarea id="adultCorruptionCustomBrief" rows="2" placeholder="描述堕落弧光，例如：清纯学妹被一步步引诱，最终主动沉沦……" style="width:100%;font-size:0.75rem;padding:6px 8px;border-radius:6px;border:1px solid var(--color-border);background:var(--color-surface);color:var(--color-text);resize:vertical;"></textarea>
        </div>
        <div class="char-nsfw-subtitle" style="margin-bottom:4px;">生成对象（来自世界书/小说人物；主角自动排除；男角色默认不勾）</div>
        <div id="adultCorruptionTargets" class="char-corruption-targets"></div>
        <div class="char-nsfw-flavor-line" style="margin-top:8px;gap:8px;">
          <button type="button" id="btnRefreshCorruptionTargets" class="btn btn-ghost adult-btn-compact">刷新角色列表</button>
          <button type="button" id="btnGenCorruptionLore" class="btn btn-primary adult-btn-compact">生成/更新恶堕世界书</button>
          <span id="adultCorruptionTip" class="ui-status-tip" role="status" aria-live="polite"></span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <span class="char-nsfw-subtitle" style="margin-top:8px;display:block;">口味/NTL 决定人物写法，并物化为世界观载体。均不进入主角 Description。</span>
  </div>
</div>

<style is:global>
  .adult-worldframe-row {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    padding: 10px 0 12px;
    margin: 8px 0 4px;
    border-top: 1px dashed var(--color-border);
    border-bottom: 1px dashed var(--color-border);
  }
  .adult-worldframe-refresh-hint {
    flex: 1 1 100%;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .adult-config-lead {
    margin: -4px 0 14px;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }
  .adult-wv-section {
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }
  .char-nsfw-block {
    padding: 2px 0 6px;
  }
  .char-nsfw-head {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }
  .char-nsfw-label {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .adult-flavor-section,
  .adult-expression-section,
  .adult-ntl-section {
    margin-top: 12px;
    padding-top: 10px;
    border-top: 1px dashed var(--color-border);
  }
  .adult-dashed-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-top: 8px;
  }
  .adult-dashed-item {
    padding: 8px 10px;
    border: 1px dashed var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: transparent;
  }
  .adult-dashed-item-head {
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 8px;
  }
  .adult-dashed-item-meta {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 0;
  }
  .adult-dashed-item-title {
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }
  .adult-dashed-item-title .adult-dashed-tag {
    margin-left: 6px;
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }
  .adult-dashed-item-desc {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.45;
    margin-top: 3px;
  }
  .adult-dashed-item-actions {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 4px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .adult-dashed-remove {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    padding: 1px 6px;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    opacity: 0.65;
    border: none;
    background: transparent;
    cursor: pointer;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
  }
  .adult-dashed-remove:hover {
    opacity: 1;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }
  .adult-dashed-move {
    font-size: 0.65rem;
    padding: 1px 4px;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    opacity: 0.55;
    border: none;
    background: transparent;
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  .adult-dashed-move:hover { opacity: 1; }
  .adult-dashed-item textarea {
    width: 100%;
    margin-top: 6px;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    padding: 4px 7px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    border: 1px dashed var(--color-border);
    background: var(--color-bg, var(--color-surface));
    color: var(--color-text);
    resize: vertical;
    min-height: 2.2em;
  }
  .adult-dashed-add-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .adult-dashed-add-row select,
  .adult-select-compact {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 140px;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    padding: 3px 6px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    background: var(--color-surface);
    color: var(--color-text);
  }
  .adult-btn-compact {
    font-size: 0.7rem !important;
    padding: 2px 8px !important;
  }
  .adult-ntl-chips {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 4px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .char-nsfw-flavor-line {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .char-nsfw-sub {
    font-size: 0.76rem;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-weight: 700;
  }
  .char-nsfw-subtitle {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    line-height: 1.4;
  }
  .char-corruption-block {
    margin-top: 12px;
    padding-top: 10px;
    border-top: 1px dashed var(--color-border);
  }
  .char-corruption-targets {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 6px 10px;
    max-height: 140px;
    overflow: auto;
    padding: 4px 0;
  }
  .char-corruption-targets label {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 4px;
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: var(--color-text);
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  .adult-wv-empty {
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    padding: 4px 0;
  }
  /* 兼容旧 class：口味/NTL 列表渲染可复用虚线卡 */
  .adult-flavor-list { display: contents; }
  .adult-flavor-item { /* unused; list uses adult-dashed-item */ }
</style>
